            <h1 class="registre-title">Registre de Prospection</h1>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">
                PÉRIODE DE STAGE : <input type="month" id="s1" style="width:130px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2)"> À <input type="month" id="s2" style="width:130px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2)">
